Package: btmembers
Title: Import Data on All Members of the Bundestag since 1949
Version: 0.0.2
Date: 2020-04-26
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Philippe",
           family = "Joly",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "philippe.joly@posteo.net",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4278-9439"))
Description: The Bundestag distributes biographical and election data on all of 
    its members since 1949 <https://www.bundestag.de/services/opendata/>. This 
    data, however, is only available in XML, a format that can be difficult to 
    work with. btmembers downloads the file "Stammdaten aller Abgeordneten seit 
    1949 im XML-Format" from the Bundestag website, converts it either to (a) 
    four data frames nested into a list (retaining all the information of the
    original XML file) or (b) a single, condensed data frame. 
